 Netherlands, this book provides insights into the polder model and the principles of pillarization in Dutch society.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aCollingwood, Vivien.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package Backlist 2002-2015z978311066278808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press  eBook Package 2015-2017z978311060644740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048524150zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789048524150.jpg  a978-3-11-060644-7  Amsterdam University Press  eBook Package 2015-2017c2015d2017  a978-3-11-066278-8  AUP eBook Package Backlist 2002-2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG